Description: Computes principal Components LEVERage (“CLEVER”), a data-driven
    measure of outlyingness for high-dimensional data such as fMRI scans. Also
    includes other quality-control measures commonly used for fMRI: framewise 
    displacement, DVARS, and anatomical CompCor.
